snippet: Hawaii will scrap a plan, announced in February, to drop the word “Rainbow” from the nickname of its men’s sports teams.
lead_paragraph: Hawaii will scrap a plan, announced in February, to drop the word “Rainbow” from the nickname of its men’s sports teams.
